Use `Settings.Add*` only in `Load(playerId)`.

| Function | Signature |
|----------|-----------|
| `Settings.AddBool` | `(key, defaultValue)` |
| `Settings.AddInt` | `(key, defaultValue, minValue, maxValue)` |
| `Settings.AddFloat` | `(key, defaultValue, minValue, maxValue)` |
