### VillagerOccupation

Constructor: `VillagerOccupation(resourceTracker)`

Methods:

- `Update()`
- `GetVillagerCount()`
- `GetVillagerCount(profession)`
- `GetAllVillagers()`
- `RequestVillagers(amount, position, urgency)`
- `SetPriorities(wood, food, gold, stone)`
- `ResetPriorities()`
